  "page": "Street of Steel",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kings_landing_map.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/4/46/Kings_landing_map.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kings_landing_map.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>1 <a href=\"/index.php/Rosby_road\" title=\"Rosby road\">Rosby road</a>, 2 <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_Gate\" title=\"Dragon Gate\">Dragon Gate</a>, 3 <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Gate\" title=\"Iron Gate\">Iron Gate</a>, 4 <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonpit\" title=\"Dragonpit\">Dragonpit</a>, 5 <a href=\"/index.php/Manse_near_the_Iron_Gate\" title=\"Manse near the Iron Gate\">Shae's manse</a>, 6 <a href=\"/index.php/Chataya%27s_brothel\" title=\"Chataya&#39;s brothel\">Chataya's brothel</a>, 7 <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Gate\" title=\"Old Gate\">Old Gate</a>, 8 <a href=\"/index.php/Flea_Bottom\" title=\"Flea Bottom\">Flea Bottom</a>, 9 <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>, 10 <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_the_Sisters\" title=\"Street of the Sisters\">Street of the Sisters</a>, 11 <a href=\"/index.php/Gate_of_the_Gods\" title=\"Gate of the Gods\">Gate of the Gods</a>, 12 <a href=\"/index.php/Cobbler%27s_Square\" title=\"Cobbler&#39;s Square\">Cobbler's Square</a>, 13 <a href=\"/index.php/Guildhall_of_the_Alchemists\" title=\"Guildhall of the Alchemists\">Guildhall of the Alchemists</a>, 14 <a href=\"/index.php/Hook\" title=\"Hook\">Hook</a>, 15 <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sept_of_Baelor\" title=\"Great Sept of Baelor\">Great Sept of Baelor</a>, 16 <a href=\"/index.php/Muddy_Way\" title=\"Muddy Way\">Muddy Way</a>, 17 <a href=\"/index.php/Fishmonger%27s_Square\" title=\"Fishmonger&#39;s Square\">Fishmonger's Square</a>, 18 <a href=\"/index.php/River_Gate\" title=\"River Gate\">River Gate</a>, 19 <a href=\"/index.php/Shop_of_Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Shop of Tobho Mott\">Tobho Mott's shop</a>, <b>20 Street of Steel</b>, 21 <a href=\"/index.php/Harbor_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Harbor of King&#39;s Landing\">harbor</a>, 22 <a href=\"/index.php/Lion_Gate\" title=\"Lion Gate\">Lion Gate</a>, 23 <a href=\"/index.php/River_Row\" title=\"River Row\">River Row</a>, 24 <a href=\"/index.php/Fish_market\" title=\"Fish market\">fish market</a>, 25 <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_grounds_(King%27s_Landing)\" title=\"Tourney grounds (King&#39;s Landing)\">tourney grounds</a>, 26 <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Gate\" title=\"King&#39;s Gate\">King's Gate</a>, 27 <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a></div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Street of Steel</b> is a street in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Geography\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Geography</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Geography\">Geography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Steel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Geography\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Street of Steel begins at the southwest corner of <a href=\"/index.php/Fishmonger%27s_Square\" title=\"Fishmonger&#39;s Square\">Fishmonger's Square</a> and curves up the western slope of <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya%27s_Hill\" title=\"Visenya&#39;s Hill\">Visenya's Hill</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sept_of_Baelor\" title=\"Great Sept of Baelor\">Great Sept of Baelor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafking.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafking.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Most smiths of the capital have their forges there. The higher up one goes, the more expensive the shops. At its top is the <a href=\"/index.php/Shop_of_Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Shop of Tobho Mott\">shop of Tobho Mott</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Steel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The young <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> once saw Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a> and his <a href=\"/index.php/Raven%27s_Teeth\" title=\"Raven&#39;s Teeth\">Raven's Teeth</a> up the Street of Steel.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> visited <a href=\"/index.php/Shop_of_Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Shop of Tobho Mott\">the shop</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Tobho Mott\">Tobho Mott</a>, where they met <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a>, one of King <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastards</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Steel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Steel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Investigating Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a>'s death, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> visits <a href=\"/index.php/Shop_of_Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Shop of Tobho Mott\">Tobho's shop</a> like his predecessor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Steel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> commands the blacksmiths of the Street of Steel to build him a great chain he will later use in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Steel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Franz_Miklis_streetofsteel.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/Franz_Miklis_streetofsteel.jpg/350px-Franz_Miklis_streetofsteel.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"264\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/Franz_Miklis_streetofsteel.jpg/525px-Franz_Miklis_streetofsteel.jpg 1.5x, /images/7/7e/Franz_Miklis_streetofsteel.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Franz_Miklis_streetofsteel.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Street of Steel, by Franz Miklis © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Ned turned off <a href=\"/index.php/Fishmonger%27s_Square\" title=\"Fishmonger&#39;s Square\">the square</a> where the Street of Steel began and followed its winding path up a long hill, past blacksmiths working at open forges, <a href=\"/index.php/Freeriders\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Freeriders\">freeriders</a> haggling over mail shirts, and grizzled <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">ironmongers</a> selling old blades and razors from their wagons. The farther they climbed, the larger the buildings grew.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Every day, every night, hammers rang along the Street of Steel, and the great chain grew longer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Steel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafking.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafking.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, King's Landing.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Eddard VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, Tyrion VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260408151013\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.034 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.035 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 688/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8954/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3691/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 860/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3521/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   18.135      1 -t